check_certificate 
  - Copyright (C) 2011, S. Zachariah Sprackett <zac@sprackett.com>


This Nagios monitor makes it possible to check for pending certificate 
expirations and receive warnings and critical notifications as appropriate.
It can be used for any TCP service that uses SSL (including https and ldaps).

The most complete and up to date information about this script can be found at:
  - http://github.com/zsprackett/check_certificate/

This document will cover how to install the script.

To install this Nagios monitor, just copy the "check_certificate" file 
to your Nagios scripts directory.
